If any student is facing any issues with their landlords not returning the deposit money or other lease-related troubles, they can call Legal Aid of Buffalo or Neighborhood Legal Services for landlord legal representation for this situation.
For students (low-income groups) this service is free, you can learn more on below contact details:
 
Legal Aid = (716) 853-9555
Neighborhood Legal Services = (716) 847-0650

Please forward as appropriate. This is from a verified source.
